# --- Runtime / scanner state ---
# The 3 small state JSONs below are TRACKED in this repo because the
# hourly GitHub Actions workflow (.github/workflows/scan.yml) commits
# them back after each run so paper-account state, signal-diff state,
# and trade history persist across runs. Local devs running the scanner
# will see them modified -- DO NOT push local state from a dev machine;
# only the github-actions[bot] commits these.
#   Propfirm Trading Dashboard/paper_trader_state.json   (TRACKED, ~300 bytes)
#   Propfirm Trading Dashboard/scan_history.json         (TRACKED, ~14 KB)
#   Propfirm Trading Dashboard/discord_state.json        (TRACKED, ~200 bytes)
# scan_results.json is regenerated every scan (~23 MB with OHLCV cache);
# never committed -- the workflow reads it within a single run only.
Propfirm Trading Dashboard/scan_results.json
Propfirm Trading Dashboard/*.log
Propfirm Trading Dashboard/**/*.log
Propfirm Trading Dashboard/*.lock

